  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3 \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d85\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0db8\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dcf \u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dd2 \u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dba \u0db1\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Turkish Airlines ground to a halt due to inefficiency of Sri Lankan staff",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A cargo plane belonging to Turkish Airlines crashed at Katunayake Airport yesterday (03) while preparing to return.",
        "This is a Turkish Airlines A.-330-300 Airbus type cargo plane. This flight TK- 6050 had arrived at Katunayake Airport on 07/03 at around 09.00 pm carrying a load of goods from Istanbul, Turkey.",
        "After that, the plane was preparing to leave Katunayake Airport for Istanbul, Turkey, carrying a 45 metric ton load of clothes manufactured by \"Victoria's Secret Stores\".",
        "At that time, due to the strong wind condition in the Katunayake airport and its surrounding area (Esala storm situation), a container that was brought to be loaded on this aircraft, the Sri Lankan Airlines airport operators did not apply brakes properly and stopped near the relevant aircraft. After being placed, the container was blown towards the plane by the strong wind and collided with its engine.",
        "Due to this incident, the right side engine number 02 of this aircraft has been damaged.",
        "As such, the necessary steps have not been taken by the Turkish aviation authorities to restore the damaged engine of this plane or leave Katunayake airport.",
        "Katunayake Airport Sri Lankan Airline's inefficient and irresponsible action of the airport staff (Bad Ground Handling) and because it is no longer possible to get fuel for its planes from Katunayake Airport in Sri Lanka, Turkish Airlines to suspend flight operations with Sri Lanka. Airport sources have revealed that the aviation authorities are currently considering."
      ],
